title: 37: OBITCH go out with a bang..
description:
In yet another chaotic installment, this week your hosts with the most are taking you through spontaneous human combustion, and a part two of poisons, oh baby radium gives you wings. We’ve got an obituary for an icon and a man who has the right idea about how to live life. OH, we almost forgot, we’ve also got some dumb.ass.criminalllllllls!
